ition - and the only woman to ever land a 900.\", \"from\": 1240, \"to\": 1356, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the only woman\", \"from\": 1247, \"to\": 1261}, {\"ngram\": \"a 720 (two complete rotations\", \"from\": 1270, \"to\": 1299}, {\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 1304, \"to\": 1315}, {\"ngram\": \"the only woman\", \"from\": 1322, \"to\": 1336}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's like, almost just normal to be honest,\\\" said her father Simon Trew said to a reporter fromNine, an Australian network.\", \"from\": 1358, \"to\": 1482, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1463, \"end\": 1473, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9923558932116284, \"rank\": 0.007702194242283947, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her father\", \"from\": 1409, \"to\": 1419}, {\"ngram\": \"Simon Trew\", \"from\": 1420, \"to\": 1430}, {\"ngram\": \"a reporter fromNine\", \"from\": 1439, \"to\": 1458}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We watch her skate every day, and we watch her just do these tricks and watch her practice these tricksall day.We watch her fall and get up and just jump back out and do it again.\\\"\", \"from\": 1483, \"to\": 1664, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her skate\", \"from\": 1493, \"to\": 1502}, {\"ngram\": \"these tricks\", \"from\": 1539, \"to\": 1551}, {\"ngram\": \"her practice\", \"from\": 1562, \"to\": 1574}, {\"ngram\": \"her fall\", \"from\": 1604, \"to\": 1612}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His wife Aiko Trew was right by his side, holding up a poster with their daughter's name on it.\", \"from\": 1665, \"to\": 1760, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1674, \"end\": 1678, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aiko_(singer)\", \"score\": 0.9283950465595471, \"rank\": 0.07712765957446846, \"text\": \"Aiko\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q1